s\n   - No standalone volatility scoring dimension\n   - No gap risk assessment\n\nKey Gaps Identified:\n- No preopen_auction stage at all\n- No execution_feasibility layer (thesis_right_but_untradeable_open, gap_risk_too_high, etc.)\n- Volume/turnover/volatility don't flow into legendary-investor pipeline\n- Leg ranking is pure score rank, ignoring liquidity/volatility/gap risk\n- Momentum/Wyckoff rules are absent from decision/validation\n- Freshness guard doesn't cover auction/execution data staleness\n\nRequirements:\n1. Add preopen_auction facts contract with auction_snapshots[], fact_flags{}, execution_risk_flags{}\n2. Add execution_feasibility layer: thesis_right_but_untradeable_open, gap_risk_too_high, high_open_low_rr, auction_not_confirmed\n3. Integrate volume/turnover/amplitude/volatility/gap into facts/checklist/validation\n4. Add momentum rules (trend continuation vs end-stage acceleration, distance from entry, high-consensus low-RR chase)\n5. Add Wyckoff rules (volume thrust, low-volume consolidation, false breakout, strong close but unchaseable)\n6. Improve leg ranking with liquidity/turnover/gap_risk/volatility/confirmation_quality\n7. Extend freshness guard to auction/execution data\n8. Maintain degraded mode consistency\n\nAnalyze from multiple angles: technical feasibility, architecture impact, performance, risks, and propose multiple solution approaches with pros/cons.\n</TASK>\nOUTPUT: Multi-angle analysis with solution approaches and trade-offs. DO NOT modify any files.\n","images":[],"local_images":[],"text_elements":[]}}
